See <er>Chagrin</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To excite ill-humor in;
to vex; to mortify; <as>as, he was not a little
<ex>chagrined</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

